    heading="Multi-environment scaling. One platform, many worlds."
    body="Agents operate across local, Docker, cloud, and hierarchical environments simultaneously. The provider system lets one Codebolt instance treat another as a coordinated environment вҖ” spawning, monitoring, and transferring state between them. Each environment runs its own agent instances with heartbeat monitoring and full lifecycle management. Build once, deploy everywhere."
