"
  />
  <FeatureBlock
    heading="Agent Deliberation Council"
    body="Agents can propose options, debate, vote, and reach consensus. The deliberation system supports decision, review, brainstorm, approval, and vote types. This is how agents make architectural decisions together вҖ” not by one agent guessing, but by multiple agents reasoning and agreeing. The system logs every deliberation for full traceability."
