Agents discuss tradeoffs
      вҶ“
Vote: 3 for option 1, 2 for option 2
      вҶ“
Consensus reached. Decision logged.
"
  />
  <FeatureBlock
    heading="Drift tracking catches what code review can't."
    body="The drift engine evaluates structural, scope, constraint, and coverage drift at two levels: local Rust assessment within each agent context, and global JavaScript coordination across all agents. When agents deviate from the original intent, the system flags it before the deviation compounds. This is how you maintain coherence across 50 agents working simultaneously."
