"
  />
  <FeatureBlock
    heading="Every decision is traceable and replayable."
    body="The Rust-based Narrative Engine captures the full reasoning chain for every agent action. Per-thread git history with snapshot versioning. Agent attribution for every change вҖ” what changed, why, and by which agent. You can replay any decision, audit any change, and understand exactly why your codebase looks the way it does. This is what makes enterprise deployment possible."
