- Agent role: junior
- Environment: production
- Risk classification: HIGH
      вҶ“
Decision: DENY
Escalate to human: ASK
      вҶ“
All decisions logged + auditable
"
  />
  <FeatureBlock
    heading="Three-tier memory. Because context is everything."
    body="Episodic memory provides time-based recall of past interactions. Persistent memory stores structured knowledge with chunking, embedding, and retrieval pipelines. The Context Assembly Engine assembles optimal context from all memory types using rules, pipelines, and token budgets. Agents don't just remember вҖ” they know what to remember."
